abstract: Greg Owen and Fabian Gomez share lead at St Jude Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Owen and Gomez each shot a three-under-par 67 to share a one-stroke lead after 54 holes at the St. Jude Classic in Memphis.

headline.main: Greg Owen and Fabian Gomez Share Lead in St. Jude
headline.print_headline: Two Share Lead in St. Jude
